title: Watch the cast of 30 Rock reunite to celebrate Tracy Morgan's Saturday Night Live return - 30 Rock US TV
text: Tracy Morgan had a little help from his 30 Rock family when making his Saturday Night Live return yesterday (October 17).The actor made his comedy comeback more than a year after he was seriously injured in a New Jersey car crash.Tracy Morgan is back on form as he promises to get 30 Rock pregnant in first SNL promosMorgan, who received an amazing reception from the audience, introduced a sketch of a 30 Rock episode apparently from 2012, which predicted his near-death experience.Tina Fey, Alec Baldwin, Jack McBrayer and Jane Krakowski reunited and reprised their roles from the NBC sitcom. Earlier in his monologue, Morgan joked: "People are wondering, 'Can he speak? Does he have 100% mental capacity?', but the truth is I never did. I might actually be a few points higher now."Saturday Night Live airs on NBC in the US.
